<h4>Using a HTTP proxy</h4>

<blockquote>
<pre>
control = HTTPPluginControl.getConnectionDefaults()
control.setProxyServer("localhost", 8001)
</pre>
</blockquote>

<p>Setting HTTP proxy authentication:</p>

<blockquote>
<pre>
connection = HTTPPluginControl.getThreadConnection("http://localhost:8001")
connection.addBasicAuthorization("proxyrealm", "phil", "password")
</pre>
</blockquote>

<p>(must be done from a worker thread.</p>

<h4>Disabling persistent connections</h4>
<blockquote>
<pre>
control = HTTPPluginControl.getConnectionDefaults()
control.setDefaultHeaders(NVPair("Connection", "close"),))
</pre>
</blockquote>



